Package: MethylBioPaths
Type: Package
Title: MethylBiopaths: Biological Pathway Analysis of Methylation Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Juan", "De Los Rios", email = "juan.delosrios@mail.utoronto.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Juan De Los Rios <juan.delosrios@mail.utoronto.ca>
Description: This package facilitates the analysis of DNA methylation data by providing functions that analyze the biological pathways enriched by the methylation driver genes in a given dataset and analyze the relationship between each driver gene's differential methylation values and each gene's mutation type.
